snippet.title: TV Game Jam - Samurai Sam Trailer
snippet.description:
Samurai Sam
https://securas.itch.io/samurai-sam

A game made for the TV Game Jam, 2019 (https://itch.io/jam/tvgamejam)
This game was strongly inspired by the animation series, Samurai Jack

Credits:
Securas (@Securas2010) Code, Art and SFX
Mark Sparling (@Markymark665) Original Music
DBR (@player_dbr) Title Art
